data.description: Welcome to this custom built 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home near the heart of DeRidder! The main living area offers an open concept and includes a formal dining area. The kitchen features granite countertops, and a moveable center island. The home offers a split floor plan. A spacious owner's suite, complete with an ensuite bathroom, double vanities and a large soaking tub. Crown molding, tray ceilings and granite throughout. Built in 2018, it sits on just under a half acre of land with a 2 car attached garage. This home has it all!
